sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Server
    participant DB

    User->>Browser: open /accounts/register
    Browser->>Server: GET /accounts/register
    Server-->>Browser: render registration form

    User->>Browser: fill and submit form
    Browser->>Server: POST /accounts/register
    Server->>Server: validate form
    alt valid
        Server->>DB: create User
        DB-->>Server: user instance
        Server-->>Browser: login and redirect to dashboard
    else invalid
        Server-->>Browser: render form with validation errors
    end
